This project includes code derived from seo-graph
(https://github.com/jdevalk/seo-graph), Copyright (c) Joost de Valk,
licensed under the MIT License.

Derived portions include the schema.org graph builders and assembler
(packages/core/src/schema/), the collection markdown alternate renderer,
aggregator, git-lastmod, IndexNow, content helpers, schema endpoint
factories, and API catalog modules, along with their tests.

The remainder of the codebase (the built-HTML agent markdown pipeline,
route mapping, manifests, llms.txt generation, Astro build integration,
and Cloudflare content-negotiation handler) is original work by Ian
Nuttall, first developed for seoskill.dev.
